<F P=100> NEAR EAST &amp; SOUTH ASIA </F>
<F P=101> EGYPT </F>
<H3> <TI>   Five `Major' Drug Dealers Arrested </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC3001115994 Cairo AL-WAFD in Arabic 24 Jan 94 p 8 </F>
<F P=103> NC3001115994 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo AL-WAFD </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] The Cairo Antinarcotics Department has arrested 
five major drug dealers, including a woman. They were found in 
possession of large amounts of hashish bags, bango plants, and 
heroin and opium, with an estimated value of half a million 
pounds. The suspects have been sent to the relevant prosecution 
office, which ordered their detention for four days, pending 
investigation. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

