<H3> <TI>   Police Seize 50,000 Mandrax Tablets in Cape Town Raid </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB2601084094 Johannesburg SAPA in English 0027 GMT 26 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> MB2601084094 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg SAPA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cape Town Jan 25 SAPA -- Police seized 50,000 
mandrax tablets with a street value of almost R[rand]1 million 
on Tuesday evening during a raid on a Grassy Park, Cape Town 
house, SABC [South African Broadcasting Corporation] radio news 
reports. 
  Seven people, including two women and a Johannesburg man, 
were arrested during the operation by members of the Wynberg 
Narcotics Bureau. 

</TEXT>

