<H3> <TI>   More Than 6 Kg of Cocaine Hydrochloride Seized in Almagro </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY2701141694 </F>
<F P=103> PY2701141694 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
Article   Type:BFN 

  [Editorial Report] Buenos Aires LA NACION in Spanish on 16 
January in Section 1, page 16, publishes an unattributed 
250-word article that says police Antidrug Squad agents arrested 
Luis Alberto Cayo Velazco with more than 6 kg of cocaine 
hydrochloride during an operation at the corner of Humahuaca and 
Gascon Streets in Almagro. Velazco was arrested while waiting to 
pass the cocaine to a contact who never appeared. Agents had 
been watching the house where the delivery was supposed to have 
taken place for two months. 

</TEXT>

