<F P=100> CHINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Results of `Special Effort' Against Drug, Weapons Trafficking in Yunnan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94P30024A Kunming YUNNAN GONGAN BAO in Chinese 30 Nov 93 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94P30024A </F>
<F P=104>  Kunming YUNNAN GONGAN BAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Summary] Yunnan's public security apparatus on 1 October 
1993 began a special effort against narcotics and weapons 
trafficking. Since October, public security components 
throughout the province have emphasized investigating and 
solving cases. By 31 October, they had solved 3358 cases of all 
types, of which 1224 were major cases, achieving a success rate 
of 76 percent and apprehending 4233 criminals. In the special 
effort, public security components have solved 463 narcotics 
cases, seizing 303.3 kg of heroin and other refined narcotics 
and 190.1 kg of opium. They have also seized 180 guns of all 
types and 663 rounds of ammunition. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

