<F P=100> CHINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yunnan Border Guards' Narcotics, Weapons Seizures Reported </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94P30025A Kunming YUNNAN GONGAN BAO in Chinese 16 Nov 93 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 94P30025A </F>
<F P=104>  Kunming YUNNAN GONGAN BAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Summary] The Armed Police Yunnan border guard division has 
produced good results in the effort against narcotics and 
weapons trafficking. According to incomplete statistics, 
between November 1992 and August 1993, this division solved over 
600 cases involving smuggling, gun-running, and narcotics 
trafficking. It seized over 350 kg of heroin, 499 kg of opium, 
385 guns of all types (including military guns), 49,467 rounds 
of ammunition, 397 hand grenades, 116 land mines, and 12 40-mm 
rocket launchers. It also seized 2,244 g of gold, 500 g of 
silver, automobiles, motorcycles, and other smuggled goods. The 
total value of seized items has exceeded 4 million yuan, and 984 
criminals have been caught. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

