<H3> <TI>   Karam Agency Political Administration Seizes 1,399 Kg of Heroin </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WD0099B Peshawar MASHRIQ in Urdu 2 Nov 93 p 12 </F>
<F P=103> 94WD0099B </F>
<F P=104>  Peshawar MASHRIQ </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Urdu </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [News Report: "Karam Agency Administration Carries Out </F>
Successful Raid on Drug Smugglers; 1399 Kilograms of Heroin and 
the Pick-Up Truck Used for Smuggling Were Seized."] 
  [Text] Peshawar (MASHRIQ News): The political 
administration of Karam Agency has seized 1,399 kilograms of 
heroin worth millions of rupees, as well as the pickup truck 
used to smuggle the narcotics. According to details received, 
the Agency's political agent was informed that certain 
international smugglers would smuggle a large quantity of heroin 
from Ilaqa Ghair to Bando Basti Ilaqa and from there to foreign 
countries. A raiding party was formed under the supervision of 
assistant political agent, Abdullah Khan. In the Khoidad Kheel 
police station area, the raiding party signalled a pickup truck, 
number KAW8503, to stop. At that time the smugglers riding in 
the truck started firing on the levy force. When the levy force 
fired back, the smugglers left the truck and ran away. A search 
of the truck produced 1,399 kilograms of heroin. The political 
administration has seized the pickup and its cargo and started 
an investigation. 

</TEXT>

