Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Smugglers' Fiasco"] </F>
  [Text] Igor Parashchak, head of the Lvov Oblast Ukrainian 
Security Service [SBU] press center, said that for the first 
time ever, two individuals, both Lvov residents, were detained 
on the border between Ukraine and Russia attempting to smuggle 
almost 30 kg of narcotic poppy straw. Their plans were foiled 
by agents from the Lvov Oblast Ukrainian Security Service 
