proved beyond any doubt in court. In a verdict announced last 
week, M.I. Kotov and M.V. Kanunnykov were sentenced, 
respectively, to 11 years in a maximum-security labor facility 
and seven years in a maximum-security correctional facility. 
The personal property of the convicts was confiscated. 
