  [Text] After three months of extensive searching, the 
various departments of the general administration for narcotics, 
in cooperation with security officers from Bani Suwayf and 
al-Minya, succeeded in seizing 20 kilograms of heroin amounting 
to 25 million pounds. An Egyptian belonging to the 
international mafia gangs was trying to smuggle the heroin to 
flood the governorates with the white poison. The car is a 
public sector car registered to an iron-casting company in Aswan. 
  The operation to seize the vehicle took place after tracking 
and pursuing them for over 750 kilometers starting from Idfu in 
Aswan up to Cairo. 

