<H3> <TI>   2.5 Tonnes of Hashish Seized in Van Province </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0502091594 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1000 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA0502091594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


