Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Van, Feb 3 (AA) -- 2.5 tonnes of hashish, hidden in 
91 sacks were seized in Baskale township in eastern Van Province 
on Wednesday. 
  AA was told that security forces acting on a tip off staged 
an operation in Sinova region in Ekecek village in Baskale 
