have foiled an attempt to smuggle 50 kg of hashish to Saudi 
Arabia. The customs officers at the airport discovered a 
quantity of hashish carefully wrapped in nylon bags and covered 
with linen cloth at the bottom of each of four tins of cheese. 
  Three Lebanese citizens were immediately detained for 
